<br>
The guy in question insisted on Alpha Loot when we'd been Master Looting, then looted out of turn a few times.  The person keeping track of whose loot it was decided to skip him twice because he looted out of turn twice.  That's when this guy told the group &quot;that's gay!&quot;<br>
<br>
I said, &quot;I'm gay.  Watch your tongue.&quot;  (I realize that, to some, that's going to be considered an &quot;attack&quot; or that I'm  an &quot;arrogant asshole&quot; for saying anything about it.)<br>
<br>
Another person in my group really let him have it, though.  I mean, really let him have it.<br>
<br>
Then he tried to say he didn't mean it as &quot;an insult&quot;, that he meant it as &quot;you know, like gay meaning dumb!&quot;<br>
<br>
Oy. <p><center><img src="http://home.earthlink.net/~andersonrob/lasgalensig.jpg" border="0"></center>
