<br>
Ignorance does not equal jerk.  It's when you try to enlighten someone and they choose to remain ignorant that they can become a jerk <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
